","score":2},{"id":"rec0rm6yYA4YUQrkh","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"Judah (patriarch)","slug":"judah_1751","score":2},{"id":"recOW0FKyYhhTt7vV","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Gihon","slug":"gihon_473","score":3},{"id":"recav9zHYvduqB2c5","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Serpent's Stone","slug":"serpents_stone_1051","score":1},{"id":"recHhcgUHKjNOWICz","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"En-rogel","slug":"en-rogel_395","score":1}],"links":[{"source":"rec4djrICdGSICvxX","target":"reconzJEzr8kOsb3j","label":"part of"},{"source":"rec4djrICdGSICvxX","target":"rec0BAacWSGBXZ0zI","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec4djrICdGSICvxX","target":"recMIpVUk92YKxyNs","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec4djrICdGSICvxX","target":"rec1ZMFtfbEvoGC73","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec4djrICdGSICvxX","target":"rec2OlshepuMiuLDJ","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec4djrICdGSICvxX","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec4djrICdGSICvxX","target":"recil8ETKDbAGI4uh","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec4djrICdGSICvxX","target":"recYR95Wl2gTyPZHl","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec4djrICdGSICvxX","target":"recYyeczKVbq0DLzk","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec4djrICdGSICvxX","target":"rec48avi3AS18d5V6","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec4djrICdGSICvxX","target":"recpvlXkEN7EVeDZn","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec4djrICdGSICvxX","target":"reci5XsSfPw9RZWBA","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec4djrICdGSICvxX","target":"reckpGvSmhqpHrvu6","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec4djrICdGSICvxX","target":"rec9SBAe047BwzwYS","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec4djrICdGSICvxX","target":"rec0rm6yYA4YUQrkh","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec4djrICdGSICvxX","target":"recOW0FKyYhhTt7vV","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec4djrICdGSICvxX","target":"recav9zHYvduqB2c5","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec4djrICdGSICvxX","target":"recHhcgUHKjNOWICz","label":"mentions"}],"verses":[{"id":"recmCkLvUxpY51bJB","ref":"1Kgs.1.1","text":"Now king David was old and stricken in years; and they covered him with clothes, but he gat no heat.","year":-1015},{"id":"reckdZkNk43koX9gT","ref":"1Kgs.1.2","text":"Wherefore his servants said unto him, Let there be sought for my lord the king a young virgin: and let her stand before the king, and let her cherish him, and let her lie in thy bosom, that my lord the king may get heat.","year":-1015},{"id":"recBCthvGStSRfwTt","ref":"1Kgs.1.3","text":"So they sought for a fair damsel throughout all the coasts of Israel, and found Abishag a Shunammite, and brought her to the king.","year":-1015},{"id":"recHtUeoXvTQ9Lm4h","ref":"1Kgs.1.4","text":"And the damsel was very fair, and cherished the king, and ministered to him: but the king knew her not.","year":-1015},{"id":"recnvHLRJI9WRET1f","ref":"1Kgs.1.5","text":"Then Adonijah the son of Haggith exalted himself, saying, I will be king: and he prepared him chariots and horsemen, and fifty men to run before him.","year":-1015},{"id":"rec9lN7bK2L1Hle1n","ref":"1Kgs.1.6","text":"And his father had not displeased him at any time in saying, Why hast thou done so? and he also was a very goodly man; and his mother bare him after Absalom.","year":-1015},{"id":"recJnM2DolAr42XnQ","ref":"1Kgs.1.7","text":"And he conferred with Joab the son of Zeruiah, and with Abiathar the priest: and they following Adonijah helped him.","year":-1015},{"id":"recT5kH2z7CdA1sdF","ref":"1Kgs.1.8","text":"But Zadok the priest, and Benaiah the son of Jehoiada, and Nathan the prophet, and Shimei, and Rei, and the mighty men which belonged to David, were not with Adonijah.","year":-1015}]}
